amilies of problems to be studied, thereby establishing large\nuniversality classes for quantum search, which we verify with extensive\nsimulations. The methods we develop could point the way towards systematic\nstudies of universality classes in computational complexity to enable\nmodification and control of search behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Aug 2017 15:49:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Feb 2018 14:28:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 Jul 2018 12:20:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-19"}
